        void buildTx(TransactionalNodeStore<USERKEY,STOREKEY,VALUE> tx)
        The callback routine that builds up a subtransaction. When this method returns the tx parameter is merged into this TransactionalNodeStore.
        Parameters:
        tx - An empty transaction that will be merged into the parent transaction.
